戲機，然后買自己最想要的幾款遊戲。有網友表示&ldquo;我要買機票去日本！和小姐姐一起打遊戲！&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T13:00:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"409159b9f209bba57405bfdaf1e3bb9834325cc8","tid":2514661,"uid":22701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T13:04:59.000Z","msg":"係咪應該問我俾3萬￥你，你可以為我做啲咩？"},{"pid":"3e86f5918671bc0027b7252ad08ffcddb9d620aa","tid":2514661,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T13:08:52.000Z","msg":"最尾條女好鬼似fc2拍過中出片嘅一條女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dc54657296ee932f3e271ac69eae18e0846a27d","tid":2514661,"uid":159083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T13:10:21.000Z","msg":"睇錯左3萬日元可以叫佢地做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e195a2301778721757978ba92677f55402bb4aa9","tid":2514661,"uid":154255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a2b88e25c09810a9ff48db43af7cb36690d8b7a","tid":2514661,"uid":44458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T12:57:11.000Z","msg":"得第一個女仔靚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T13:12:05.000Z","msg":"邊度？睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae616eb026fac80f560b4676b624a49eac676ab5","tid":2514661,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T13:14:49.000Z","msg":"3萬yen ，算把啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}